Angular PWA
~~~~~~~~~~~~
1. Include Angular PWA in a project using the below command

    ng add @angular/pwa@18.0.0   

2. Install http server using the below command

    npm i -g http-server

3. Build the Angular application 
4. Use the below command to serve the built Angular application

    http-server dist/nfex-sample/browser

5. Access the application on the http server
6. Kill the http-server
7. Access the application in the same url as above. The app should load as though the server is alive
